948","tid":1758861,"uid":85509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:57:12.000Z","msg":"工作上接觸過大陸人<br />\n接觸果啲多數都係八十後大學畢業<br />\n佢地可以話係對政府敢怒不敢言<br />\n平時朋友間吹水屌中共都多<br />\n佢地都話佢地根本冇能力改變中國政治環境<br />\n一公開表態輕則冇左份工<br />\n重則家破人亡<br />\n所以唔會放精力落去政治<br />\n只係過下日晨 得閒去旅行就已經心滿意足<br />\n<br />\n香港現有嘅自由對佢地黎講已經非常自由<br />\n佢地都好羨慕 <br />\n對佢地黎講 香港嘅運動令香港失色<br />\n益撚左新加坡<br />\n覺得可惜"},{"pid":"42207d49546bef810a33619dbe6bc85e0b033612","tid":1758861,"uid":181502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821c0938adc05f3ac3035605ddc2d691c62196a0","tid":1758861,"uid":53672,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"咪安慰自己啦 事實就係90%都係5毛紅衛兵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:57:25.000Z","msg":"又想借啲意講埋啲咩輸出革命，實質就係想分薄本土嘅抗爭能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2bc1d63e2c70d50679271edddbae95513452ed","tid":1758861,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4314079f093b9b07abfad0674d20298b4dea26a4","tid":1758861,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e387b0924b93ef5450d09d5c7f525e5f08f07768","tid":1758861,"uid":149496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"821c0938adc05f3ac3035605ddc2d691c62196a0","tid":1758861,"uid":53672,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T10:18:46.000Z","msg":"咪安慰自己啦 事實就係90%都係5毛紅衛兵"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:50:07.000Z","msg":"係你上網睇先咁覺得遮 俾得你睇嘅都係撐共 反共嗰啲好快刪走 仲有五毛引導輿論 即係帶風向"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"佢地90後同00後大部份民族主義上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"佢哋將中國=中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f5123d9d887792